name: Empire In The Sky (Canceled)
blurb: Empire In The Sky is a cartoon video game set in "The Future" - in space.  You patrol the galaxy, exploring the universe.  Play with your friends.

rewards.reward: WEE BACKER: Any backer who pays $30 or more would get a free copy of the game once it is released. All backers regardless of their contribution over the minimum $10 have an option to become a beta tester and try the game before it is released. All beta testers will be listed in the credits on the website.

CYBORG: $50 or more could get you an "improved" starting ship code, the ability to beta-test the game before it is released, and your name appears in the website credits for beta-testers. The starting ship code gives the player a slightly improved starting ship and a unique in-game radio taunt that only "improved" starting ship code possessors have.

SPACE PIRATE: $100 or more could get you a different level of involvement, providing you with your name in the credits of the actual game, the ability to beta test, a custom starting ship, and a planetoid named after you that appears in the static game world. Planetoids are asteroids and other sub-planetary bodies (moons and comets) that exist in the galactic slice that the players play in. \r\nYou also get a T-Shirt (or Hoodie) with the game's title OR a nice Mug to enjoy your tasty beverage.

STARBLAZER: For $250 or more, you could have a star named after you, optionally 1 additional planet, planetoid or moon body named after you or a member of your family or friends, the chance to beta-test the game (with your name in the website credits) and an "improved" starting ship code. Additionally at the $250, your name would appear on the actual in-game credits that are shown during the title sequence / main menu. You also get a T-Shirt (or Hoodie) with the game's title and a nice Mug to enjoy your tasty beverage.

STELLAR CELEB: For $300 or you will appear in the Galactic Annals on Starbase Central (an in-game hub) with a spiffy title of your choosing (as long as it is not offensive) or our choosing if you so wish. You also receive an "improved" starting ship code with unique radio taunt, your name appears in the beta-tester credits on the website, you get to have a star, planet and moon named after you, your family members or a friend. Your name would also appear in the in-game credits. \r\nYou also get a T-Shirt (or Hoodie) with the game's title and a nice Mug to enjoy your tasty beverage.

OLD ONE: Folks who donate amounts equal to or greater than $500 are given all of the benefits of the other tiers (name appears in Galactic Annals on Starbase Central with spiffy title, "improved" starting ship code, improved starting ship taunt, a star, planet, moon named after you or your friends and family. They also receive 1 high level character of their design and custom graphic (made by us or them at their discretion). The high level character will be a completed character with access to all of the end-game features, with the ability to run a team / guild / company, and $1M space bucks. Your name would also appear on the in-game credits. \r\nYou also get a T-Shirt (or Hoodie) with the game's title and a nice Mug to enjoy your tasty beverage.

PRECURSOR: At the $1000 level, you receive everything that a $500 backer gets (beta testing, three celestial bodies named after you, your friends or family members, Galactic Annal entry, in-game credits mention, "improved starting ship code", on-website beta testing credits mention, high level completed character and $1M space bucks) and also 1 computer generated alien species named after you or named by your choosing (as long as the name isn't infringing, offensive etc). Optionally, we can create your alien species name for you based on your name. You can give a free copy of the game to up to 5 friends and hey, and as an added incentive, we'll name a nebula after you, too. \r\nYou also get a T-Shirt (or Hoodie) with the game's title and a nice Mug to enjoy your tasty beverage.

RAT PACK: For $2000 bucks you can have everything in the PRECURSOR level, plus 5 extra copies (for a total of 10 accounts), our undying love and devotion, and a whole sector named after you. Your Galactic Annal entry will be at the top of the list. There are only 5 sectors, one of which is already named, so only 4 people can buy into this status. If no more sectors are available when you back us with this much dough, we'll let you name every single object in one entire solar system... of your choosing! (Aside from the Earth system) This could mean up to 100 objects each named after your friends, relatives and pets. (With their permission, of course.) We'll send you a picture of the system and all the objects for you to name. We'll also throw in a special in-game StarCard worth $10M space bucks on your primary account. \r\nYou also get a T-Shirt (or Hoodie) with the game's title and a nice Mug to enjoy your tasty beverage.
